01:22:24,890 --> 01:22:25,640
你來幹嘛  王爾德
What's it to you, Wilde?

1341
01:22:25,640 --> 01:22:27,890
不用搗鼓爪子冰棒了嗎
Shouldn't you be melting down a Pawpsicle or something?

1342
01:22:28,480 --> 01:22:30,430
這不是兔兔警官嗎
if it isn't flopsy the copsie.

1343
01:22:30,430 --> 01:22:33,720
我們已經知道了  你偷的根本不是洋蔥
We both know those weren't only onions I caught you stealing.

1344
01:22:33,730 --> 01:22:36,070
你要午夜嚎叫幹什麼  猥瑣屯
What were you gonna do with those Night Howlers, Weselton?

1345
01:22:36,070 --> 01:22:40,290
是黃鼠狼  黃鼠狼公爵  我才不告訴你呢  兔子
It's Weaselton, Duke Weaselton. And I ain't talking, rabbit.

1346
01:22:40,290 --> 01:22:42,910
你能逼我還是怎麼著
And there ain't nothing you can do to make me.

1347
01:22:44,270 --> 01:22:45,570
做了他
Ice him.

1348
01:22:48,710 --> 01:22:51,160
死耗子  幹嘛幫她  她是警察
You dirty rat, why are you helping her? She's a cop!

1349
01:22:51,160 --> 01:22:54,340
她還是我未來外孫女的教母
And the godmother to my future granddaughter.

1350
01:22:54,340 --> 01:22:56,660
我打算叫她朱迪
I'm gonna name her Judy.

1351
01:22:57,840 --> 01:22:59,580
做了這只黃鼠狼
Ice this weasel.

1352
01:22:59,580 --> 01:23:01,780
不要  求你了  我什麼都說
All right, all right! Please! I'll talk. I'll talk.

1353
01:23:01,780 --> 01:23:03,590
