They offered me what I couldn't refuse: Money.

1355
01:23:06,660 --> 01:23:08,750
你把那些花兒賣給誰了
And to whom did you sell them?

1356
01:23:08,750 --> 01:23:10,160
一隻叫道格的公羊
A ram named Doug.

1357
01:23:10,160 --> 01:23:11,920
我們在地下有個交易點
We got a drop spot underground.

1358
01:23:11,940 --> 01:23:15,130
一定要小心  道格絕不是善類
Just watch it. Doug is the opposite of friendly.

1359
01:23:12,210 --> 01:23:15,040
{\an8}榕樹街地鐵站

1360
01:23:15,500 --> 01:23:17,310
他一點都不友好
He's unfriendly.

1361
01:23:27,600 --> 01:23:28,510
趕緊地
Come on.

1362
01:23:41,980 --> 01:23:43,790
黃鼠狼沒有說謊
The weasel wasn't lying.

1363
01:23:43,790 --> 01:23:46,860
道格壟斷了整個午夜嚎叫的市場
Yeah,it looks like old Doug's cornered the market on Night Howlers.

1364
01:24:30,980 --> 01:24:33,610
我是道格  目標是誰
You got Doug here. What's the mark?

1365
01:24:34,450 --> 01:24:38,640
撒哈拉廣場的獵豹  知道了
Cheetah in Sahara Square. Got it.

1366
01:24:39,100 --> 01:24:41,960
什麼  我知道他們很快  但我能搞定
Serious? Yeah, I know they're fast, I can hit him.

1367
01:24:41,960 --> 01:24:44,050
一隻坐在車裡的小小水獺
Listen, I hit a tiny little otter

1368
01:24:44,050 --> 01:24:46,640
我都能穿過車窗打中
through the open window of a moving car.

1369
01:24:59,990 --> 01:25:01,610
搞定了我打你電話
Yeah, I'll buzz you when it's done.

1370
01:25:01,610 --> 01:25:03,380
或者你直接看新聞
Or you'll see it on the news.

1371
01:25:03,380 --> 01:25:05,270
看那個更快了
You know, whichever comes first.

1372
01:25:05,610 --> 01:25:08,910
道格  開門  拿鐵來了
Hey, Doug, open up! We've got your latte.

1373
01:25:08,910 --> 01:25:10,550
沃爾特和傑西回來了
All right, Woolter and Jesse are back,

1374
01:25:10,550 --> 01:25:12,480
我要掛了
so I'm leaving now. Out.

1375
01:25:12,480 --> 01:25:13,150
你要去哪裡
Hey. Wait, where you going?

1376
01:25:13,150 --> 01:25:14,380
你要去哪裡  回來
Where are you going? Get back here!

1377
01:25:14,390 --> 01:25:16,540
你要幹嘛  你會被逮到的
What are you doing? He's gonna see you!

1378
01:25:17,170 --> 01:25:18,770
你在看什麼
What are you looking at? Hey!

1379
01:25:18,770 --> 01:25:20,450
不管你在想什麼  別亂來
Whatever you're thinking, stop thinking it.

1380
01:25:20,450 --> 01:25:23,610
蘿蔔頭  蘿蔔頭
Carrots. Carrots.

1381
01:25:23,840 --> 01:25:26,110
這次讓他多加奶泡了吧
You better have the extra foam this time.

1382
01:25:29,100 --> 01:25:29,840
開門
Hey! Open up!

1383
01:25:29,850 --> 01:25:32,480
你要幹嘛  你把我們困在這裡了
What are you doing? You just trapped us in here!

1384
01:25:32,480 --> 01:25:34,600
我們要把這些證據送到警局
We need to get this evidence to the ZPD.

1385
01:25:34,600 --> 01:25:37,800
-裝好了  走吧  -要所有的
- Okay, great. Here it is. Got it. - No, all of it.

1386
01:25:37,800 --> 01:25:39,190
什麼
Wait, what?

1387
01:25:42,060 --> 01:25:44,270
你都會開火車了啊
Oh, great, you're a conductor now, huh?

1388
01:25:44,270 --> 01:25:45,090
聽我說
Hey. Listen.

1389
01:25:45,090 --> 01:25:48,350
要啟動這堆廢鐵除非奇跡發生
It would take a miracle to get this rustbucket going.

1390
01:25:49,670 --> 01:25:51,570
好吧  哈利路亞
Well. Hallelujah.

1391
01:25:51,570 --> 01:25:56,180
實驗室這裡出了點狀況  是大麻煩
We kinda got a situation at the lab. It just got worse!

1392
01:25:57,510 --> 01:25:58,870
任務完成
Mission accomplished.

1393
01:25:58,870 --> 01:26:01,480
現在嘟嘟鳴笛慶祝會不會有點早
Would it be premature for me to do a little victory toot-toot?

1394
01:26:01,480 --> 01:26:04,080
好吧  就嘟一下
All right. One toot-toot.

1395
01:26:06,420 --> 01:26:09,320
又一個願望完成了
Well, I can cross that off the bucket list.

1396
01:26:19,680 --> 01:26:21,870
那聲鳴笛還是取消吧
I may have to rescind that victory toot-toot.

1397
01:26:23,970 --> 01:26:25,450
也許只是下冰雹了
Maybe that's just hail.

1398
01:26:29,140 --> 01:26:30,210
走開
Back off!

1399
01:26:35,480 --> 01:26:36,540
來了
Incoming!

1400
01:26:40,070 --> 01:26:42,030
-蘿蔔頭  -別剎車
- Carrots! - Don't stop! Keep going.

1401
01:26:42,030 --> 01:26:43,420
不  快剎車
No, stop. Please stop!

1402
01:26:43,420 --> 01:26:45,770
絕對不要剎車
Do not stop this car!

1403
01:27:07,560 --> 01:27:09,230
加快速度  尼克
Speed up, Nick. Speed up!

1404
01:27:09,240 --> 01:27:10,580
對面有另一輛列車
There's another train coming!

1405
01:27:10,580 --> 01:27:12,600
相信我  加速
Trust me, speed up.

1406
01:27:16,420 --> 01:27:17,940
停車
Stop the train!

1407
01:27:19,560 --> 01:27:21,640
要幫忙嗎
Hey. Need some help?

1408
01:27:25,300 --> 01:27:28,580
天啊  太快了  抓住
Oh, no. Oh, no no no. Too fast! Too fast! Hold on!

1409
01:27:40,560 --> 01:27:42,050
我們該下車了
I think this is our stop.

1410
01:27:51,050 --> 01:27:54,440
也許  也許還有證據留下來
Okay, maybe... Maybe some of the evidence survived.

1411
01:28:03,400 --> 01:28:06,660
全沒了  我們搞砸了
Everything is gone. We've lost it all.

1412
01:28:07,780 --> 01:28:10,710
除了這個
Yeah. All, except for this.

1413
01:28:11,320 --> 01:28:13,250
太好了  尼克
Nick! Yes!

1414
01:28:13,430 --> 01:28:15,620
走吧  我們趕緊送去警局
Come on! We gotta get to the ZPD.

1415
01:28:16,340 --> 01:28:18,290
從自然博物館穿過去
Cut through the Natural History Museum.

1416
01:28:29,990 --> 01:28:33,730
-就在那裡  -朱迪  朱迪
- There it is. - Judy. Judy!

1417
01:28:34,580 --> 01:28:36,140
頭羊市長
Mayor Bellwether.

1418
01:28:36,570 --> 01:28:37,850
我們知道真相了
We found out what's happening.

1419
01:28:37,850 --> 01:28:39,950
有人向肉食動物注射血清
Someone's darting predators with a serum.

1420
01:28:39,950 --> 01:28:41,690
所以他們才獸性大發
That's what's making them go savage.

1421
01:28:41,690 --> 01:28:45,070
幹得真棒 朱迪  我真為你驕傲
I'm so proud of you, Judy. You did just a super job.

1422
01:28:45,070 --> 01:28:46,470
謝謝市長
Thank you, ma'am.

1423
01:28:50,750 --> 01:28:52,910
你是怎麼找到我們的
How did you know where to find us?

1424
01:28:52,910 --> 01:28:54,570
我要過去拿箱子了
I'll go ahead and I'll take that case now.

1425
01:28:54,570 --> 01:28:59,900
還是我跟尼克送到警局吧
You know what? I think Nick and I will just take this to the ZPD.

1426
01:29:04,450 --> 01:29:05,520
-跑  -跑
- Run. - Run.

1427
01:29:06,660 --> 01:29:07,970
抓住他們
Get them!

1428
01:29:14,070 --> 01:29:15,140
蘿蔔頭
Carrots!

1429
01:29:16,670 --> 01:29:18,480
我來扶你  趕緊過來
Here, I got you. Get in here.

1430
01:29:20,920 --> 01:29:23,270
先放鬆下
Okay. Now, just relax.

1431
01:29:24,390 --> 01:29:26,670
-吃藍莓嗎  -不用了
- Blueberry? - Pass.

1432
01:29:28,400 --> 01:29:30,590
朱迪
Judy.

1433
01:29:30,840 --> 01:29:33,210
把箱子拿給牛局長
Take the case. Get it to Bogo.

1434
01:29:33,210 --> 01:29:35,000
我不會拋下你的
I'm not gonna leave you behind, that's not happening.

1435
01:29:35,010 --> 01:29:37,830
-我走不了  -我們會想到辦法的
- I can't walk. - Just.. We'll think of something.

1436
01:29:37,830 --> 01:29:40,260
我們都是一樣的  朱迪
We're on the same team, Judy.

1437
01:29:40,410 --> 01:29:44,550
被人低估  懷才不遇
Underestimated. Underappreciated.

1438
01:29:44,550 --> 01:29:46,890
你還沒厭倦這一切嗎
Aren't you sick of it?

1439
01:29:49,480 --> 01:29:53,340
食肉動物就算強壯嗓門大
Predators. They may be strong and loud.

1440
01:29:53,350 --> 01:29:56,740
但如果食草動物是食肉動物的十倍
But prey outnumber predators 10 to 1.

1441
01:30:00,950 --> 01:30:01,770
試想一下
Think about it.

1442
01:30:01,770 --> 01:30:07,010
百分之九十的動物聯手對付共同的敵人
90% of the population united against a common enemy.

1443
01:30:07,010 --> 01:30:09,140
我們將所向披靡
We'll be unstoppable.

1444
01:30:15,030 --> 01:30:16,100
在那裡
Over there!

1445
01:30:33,040 --> 01:30:35,680
你就該呆在胡蘿蔔農場裡
Well, you should have just stayed on the carrot farm, huh?

1446
01:30:35,960 --> 01:30:38,840
太可惜了  我挺喜歡你的
It really is too bad, I did like you.

1447
01:30:38,840 --> 01:30:41,320
你想幹嘛  殺了我嗎
What are you gonna do? Kill me?

1448
01:30:42,390 --> 01:30:44,200
當然不是了
No, of course not.

1449
01:30:44,640 --> 01:30:45,810
是他
He is.

1450
01:30:46,210 --> 01:30:48,610
不  尼克
No! Oh, Nick?

1451
01:30:49,170 --> 01:30:53,850
警官  自然歷史博物館裡有只獸性大發的狐狸
Yes, police! There's a savage fox in the Natural History Museum!

1452
01:30:53,850 --> 01:30:56,890
霍普斯警官已倒下  趕緊過來
Officer Hopps is down. Please hurry!

1453
01:30:57,360 --> 01:30:58,710
尼克  你要反抗
No, Nick. Don't do this. Fight it.

1454
01:30:58,710 --> 01:31:01,840
但他是無法反抗的
Oh, but he can't help it. Can he?

1455
01:31:01,940 --> 01:31:07,010
食肉動物的天生就有獸性
Since predators are just biologically predisposed to be savages.

1456
01:31:17,810 --> 01:31:20,490
想想明天的頭條
Gosh! Think of the headline!

1457
01:31:20,740 --> 01:31:24,410
英雄警官被獸性狐狸所殺害
Hero Cop Killed by Savage Fox.

1458
01:31:25,520 --> 01:31:26,540
你的目的就是這個嗎
So that's it?

1459
01:31:26,540 --> 01:31:29,630
食草動物畏懼食肉動物然後你掌權
Prey fears predator, and you stay in power?

1460
01:31:29,630 --> 01:31:31,250
差不多吧
Yeah. Pretty much.

1461
01:31:31,250 --> 01:31:32,570
不會得逞的
It won't work.

1462
01:31:32,570 --> 01:31:35,130
畏懼總能管用的
Fear always works.

1463
01:31:35,130 --> 01:31:38,510
為了這目的  我會給所有肉食動物都打一針
And I'll dart every predator in Zootopia to keep it that way.

1464
01:31:41,610 --> 01:31:43,970
尼克  不
Oh, Nick. No.

1465
01:31:46,940 --> 01:31:48,400
再見了  小兔子
Bye-bye, bunny.

1466
01:31:54,870 --> 01:31:59,000
流血  血  血  和死亡
Blood, blood, blood! And death.

1467
01:31:59,000 --> 01:32:00,320
好了好了  強行搶戲嗎
All right, you know you're milking it.

1468
01:32:00,320 --> 01:32:02,230
而且  我覺得我們成功了
Besides, I think we got it. I think we got it.

1469
01:32:02,230 --> 01:32:04,450
我們成功了  謝謝你  叨叨羊
We got it up there, thank you, yakety-yak.

1470
01:32:04,450 --> 01:32:06,420
你全盤招認了
You laid it all out beautifully.

1471
01:32:06,420 --> 01:32:07,100
什麼
What?

1472
01:32:07,100 --> 01:32:09,110
你是在找血清嗎
Yeah. Oh, are... are you looking for the serum?

1473
01:32:09,340 --> 01:32:10,350
在這呢
Well, it's right here.

1474
01:32:10,350 --> 01:32:11,840
你武器裡的
What you've got in the weapon there,

1475
01:32:11,930 --> 01:32:14,620
是我家裡農場種的藍莓
those are blueberries, from my family's farm.

1476
01:32:15,510 --> 01:32:17,790
可好吃了  你該嘗嘗
They are delicious. You should try some.

1477
01:32:18,290 --> 01:32:21,200
我陷害了獅心  我也可以陷害你
I framed Lionheart, I can frame you too.

1478
01:32:21,320 --> 01:32:23,810
你們空口無憑
It's my word against yours.

1479
01:32:24,330 --> 01:32:25,600
其實呢
Actually...

1480
01:32:25,820 --> 01:32:29,180
我會給所有肉食動物都打一針
And I'll dart every predator in Zootopia to keep it that way.

1481
01:32:29,180 --> 01:32:31,060
我都錄下來了
It's your word against yours.

1482
01:32:31,910 --> 01:32:34,860
這叫智取  親愛的
It's called a hustle, Sweetheart. Boom!

1483
01:32:42,170 --> 01:32:44,810
前任市長晨曦·頭羊已入獄
Former mayor, Dawn Bellwether is behind bars today,

1484
01:32:43,010 --> 01:32:49,370
{\an8}前市長頭羊入獄

1485
01:32:44,810 --> 01:32:47,120
罪名是策劃了動物城
guilty of masterminding the savage attacks

1486
01:32:47,120 --> 01:32:49,000
食肉動物野蠻襲擊事件
that have plagued Zootopia of late.

1487
01:32:49,000 --> 01:32:51,180
她的前任上司  裡奧多·獅心
Her predecessor, Leodore Lionheart,

1488
01:32:50,140 --> 01:33:03,540
{\an8}獅心終於發聲

1489
01:32:51,180 --> 01:32:53,010
否認所有與其密謀的指控
denies any knowledge of her plot,

1490
01:32:53,010 --> 01:32:55,600
聲稱只是為了保護動物城
claiming he was just trying to protect the city.

1491
01:32:55,600 --> 01:32:58,040
我囚禁這些動物是錯的嗎
Did I falsely imprison those animals?

1492
01:32:58,120 --> 01:32:59,630
是的  我確實錯了
Well, yes. Yes, I did.

1493
01:32:59,630 --> 01:33:00,510
這是經典的
It was a classic

1494
01:33:00,510 --> 01:33:03,490
為了正確的目的做了錯事
doing the wrong thing for the right reason kind of a deal.

1495
01:33:03,490 --> 01:33:05,230
另外  醫生宣稱
In related news, doctors say

1496
01:33:04,090 --> 01:33:08,490
{\an8}午夜嚎叫解藥已見成效

1497
01:33:05,230 --> 01:33:07,890
午夜嚎叫的解藥
the Night Howlers' antidote is proving effective

1498
01:33:07,890 --> 01:33:10,660
已讓受害食肉動物逐漸恢復
in rehabilitating the afflicted predators.

1499
01:33:15,780 --> 01:33:18,050
艾米特
Oh, Emmitt!

1500
01:33:21,410 --> 01:33:22,630
謝謝
Thank you.

1501
01:33:25,380 --> 01:33:26,810
我小時候
When I was a kid,

1502
01:33:27,340 --> 01:33:31,040
我以為動物城是完美的地方
I thought Zootopia was this perfect place.

1503
01:33:31,040 --> 01:33:33,010
人人和諧相處
Where everyone got along,

1504
01:33:33,310 --> 01:33:35,940
誰都能成就無限可能
and anyone could be anything.

1505
01:33:36,620 --> 01:33:37,850
現在發現
Turns out,

1506
01:33:38,140 --> 01:33:39,990
現實遠比宣傳口號
real life is a little bit more complicated

1507
01:33:39,990 --> 01:33:42,300
要複雜
than a slogan on a bumper sticker.

1508
01:33:42,790 --> 01:33:45,030
現實生活是糟糕的
Real life is messy.

1509
01:33:45,990 --> 01:33:48,380
我們都有局限性
We all have limitations.

1510
01:33:48,530 --> 01:33:50,200
都會犯錯
We all make mistakes.

1511
01:33:50,200 --> 01:33:54,370
但是樂觀點來說  我們也都很像
Which means, hey, glass half full, we all have a lot in common.

1512
01:33:54,690 --> 01:33:57,520
